fields.name: Small adventure harness
fields.description: Does your dog have a taste for exploration? This polyester Bunty Adventure Harness comes with two separate attachment points. The first A-loop on the back gives your furry friend a greater degree of freedom, while the chest-mounted ring grants the owner a greater sense of control.

fields.name: Tartan Harness from Bunty
fields.description:
Adjustable straps for a comfy fit.
Fabricated using a water-resistant material.
Offers two points of attachment – an ‘A’ loop on the back and a chest-mounted ring for varied control.
Built-in reinforced rubber handle on the back to allows you to pick up your pup quickly.
Designed with a large chest plate that provides an even spread of weight to prevent injury.
Reflective piping to ensure excellent night visibility

fields.name: Halti Nose Collar
fields.description:
The complete Stop Pulling Program! This Halti Optifit Dog Headcollar is highly adjustable and stops dogs from pulling by gently directing the head so that the body has to follow.
Specially designed to provide an ergonomic and comfortable fit, the adjustable chin-strap, with secure camlock, allows a customised fitting for every dog.

fields.name: Flashing Collar
fields.description: This great USB Rechargeable Flashing Dog Collar Band is a big help in keeping your canine friend safe on dark evening walks, creates a highly visible light that can be seen for up to 500 metres giving motorists warning of your pet's presence

fields.name: Navy Quilted Coat
fields.description: This quality  Quilt Dog Coat is perfect for keeping your dog snug, dry and warm when outdoors. It  is particularly good for smaller dogs or long haired breeds as it will protect your canine friends coat from rain, mud, snow and the elements.

fields.name: Reflective Hi-Viz Coat
fields.description: This Hi Viz Safety Dog Coat will ensure your dog is easily seen at night as well as highly visible at other times. Walking dogs at night in areas with low-lighting can be dangerous, so it is essential to provide a little extra safety in the dark to help make your canine friend more visible to drivers. A great safety dog coat at a great price.

fields.name: Danish Design 2-in-1 Coat
fields.description:
The Danish Design 2 in 1 Dog Coat is the perfect coat whatever the season.

With its removable Polar Fleece liner, this coat is superb for both the winter and warmer months. The coat is a lightweight waterproof and breathable to protect your dog from summer showers. When the weather gets cooler simply re-attach the fleece and you have a warm and waterproof all-purpose winter coat.

fields.name: Waterproof Coat
fields.description:
This All Weather Waterproof Coat is not only stylish but warm too. 

Waterproof nylon
Warm fur lining
Easy fastening Velcro strap

fields.name: Ergo  Feeder Bowl
fields.description:
The Savic Ergo Feeder 28cm is perfect for medium to larger sized dogs who have digestion problems or suffer from arthritis.

This item is assorted so we cannot offer a choice of colour.

fields.name: Gobble Stop Bowl
fields.description:
The  Gobble Stopper will instantly slow the speed at which your dog eats!
Place the Gobble Stopper disc over your dogs wet or dry food and you'll be amazed at how effective it is
This simple, yet effective, device will help to reduce belching and bloat that can be associated with pets that eat too quickly. It is simple to use, and easy to clean

fields.name: Lickimat Playdate
fields.description:
The Lickimat PlaymateTreat Mat is designed as a tasty boredom buster for your cat or dog. By spreading their favourite soft treat over its surface, you can create a fun and tasty game that will keep them licking and entertained for long periods of time.
Works well as a slow feeder
Recommended by vets and animal behaviourists

fields.name: Slow Feeder
fields.description: Turn your dog’s meal into a challenging game with this Green Slow Dog Feeder and significantly reduce the risk of ‘bloat’. It is a really simple solution to encourage a slower pace and reduce the excessive air intake that can lead to bloating or vomiting. Simply scatter the food across the feeder and watch your dog work to get at it.

fields.name: Dry Mitt
fields.description:
The Tall Tails Wet Paws Drying Mitt is a super absorbent mitt that allows you to clean your dog’s paws before they come in the house.
Super absorbent.
One size fits all hands.
Loop to hang up for convenience.
Machine wash & dry.

fields.name: Dog Grooming Brush
fields.description:
The Mikki Easy Clean Slicker has specially shaped slicker pins that retract to easily clear the slicker of dead hair so you can carry on grooming.

Removes dead hair from undercoat and top coat.
Helps brush out minor knots and tangles.
Push button quickly removes dead hair from the slicker.

fields.name: Double side Brush
fields.description:
The Rosewood Double Sided Soft Protection Salon Brush is a professional, high-quality grooming brush for your pet.

Ergonomic hand and thumb grip.
Pin Side breaks up the coat, removing loose hair and debris.
Bristle side gives that finishing touch to the coat.
Suitable for short, medium and long coats

fields.name: Zoom Groom Blue
fields.description:
The KONG Zoom Groom is an excellent grooming and shampooing brush. The rubber fingers reach through the coat to massage the skin, stimulating capillaries and natural oil production leading to a healthy coat for your dog.

Easy grip.
Patented brush comfortably massages dog during grooming.
Makes cleaning and shampooing more effective with wide bristles.
Suitable for all types of coat.

fields.name: Catch Feeder
fields.description:
The Catit Play Treat Spinner is an interactive slow feeder with dynamic treat spaces that provides your cat with hours of fun. It has a soft and flexible silicone cover that is very easy to clean.

You simply insert your cat’s favourite treat into the flower shaped top opening and let your cat do the rest.

fields.name: Cat Water Fountain
fields.description:
The Purrshire Cat Fountain provides continuous flowing water that your cat will love to drink from. Keeps water fresh
Electric pump
Double water filters
Capacity: 3 Litres

fields.name: Cat Treat Maze
fields.description: Reward your cat's curiosity with the Catit Senses Treat Maze. Stimulating for your cat and highly entertaining for you, this fun toy is a clever way for you to make your kitty work for its treats.

fields.name: Small Cat Bowl
fields.description:
Low rim so your cat can enjoy their dinner without disturbing their sensitive whiskers
Sustainable and natural bamboo, BPA FREE
Durable and long lasting. and will completely break down once disposed of
Dishwasher safe, strong and durable
Non-slip base

fields.name: Catnip Bubbles
fields.description: Give your cat bubble madness, with this fun catnip scented Cosmic Catnip Bubbles – 150ml. This unique interactive toy is a completely safe and non-toxic and makes for hilarious and crazy fun.

fields.name: Cat Tunnel
fields.description: The All For Paws Lambswool Cat Tunnel is a fabulous and fun choice for your feline friend. The tunnel design gives your cat an ideal spot to hide out or sleep in. It also features a central port hole so your cat can pop its head through, keeping an eye out for dinner time.

fields.name: Snake Teaser
fields.description:
With natural feathers and an irresistible rattle sound, this soft, plush KONG Cat Snake Teaser is a great cat toy! It has been specially designed to attract your feline friend’s attention to stimulate your cat’s hunting instinct. It features a sturdy, plush covered rod and the snake is really long!
A fabulous plaything for your pet and perfect for fun, interactive play. A portion of premium catnip has also been added to further encourage play!

fields.name: Catnip Caterpillar
fields.description: KONG Cat Nibble Critter Catnipillar Toy appeals to a cat’s natural instinctive desire to claw and bat with an easy-grip mesh fabric. The open netting material cleans and polishes teeth while allowing KONG Premium North American Catnip aromas to flow freely and stimulate a cat's natural curiosity and hunting instincts

fields.name: Hi Viz Cat Collar
fields.description: The Ancol Hi-Vis Cat Collar is a high visibility cat collar with reflective patterns that increases your cat's visibility in low light. The collar is fitted with a break-away buckle to allow your cat an easy escape if they get caught whilst climbing.

fields.name: Pink Collar with Bell
fields.description:
Reflective patters increase visibility in low light
Break-away buckle allows the cat to easily escape if caught whilst climbing
XL warning bell to help protect wildlife

fields.name: Kitten Reflective Collar
fields.description:
This Rosewood Kitten Reflective Collar is a nylon collar with a safety buckle, and elastic.  
Available in pastel blue or pink, Please note we are unable to allow customers a choice of colour on this product
Reflective design
Fully adjustable
Will accept most brands cat flap keys
Safety clasp
Dimensions: Fits neck size: approx 15-20cm

fields.name: Cat Flea Collar
fields.description: Seresto Flea & Tick Control Collar is the longest-lasting single application flea and tick protection available, giving you piece of mind for 7-8 months as one collar is all it takes to keep your cat protected.

fields.name: Travel Bowl
fields.description: A very handy addition for long and short trips. A  non-spill bowl that contain food or water for your dog.

fields.name: Pup Cover-up
fields.description:
For those cold wet days when your dog just won't leave the house -- change his mind with our Pup Cover-Up   an overall that keeps the wet and cold out and lets your pet enjoy his outing instead of hating it! 
One of our very best selling products!!

fields.name: Handi-Towel
fields.description:
The Handi-Towel  for two handed cleaning is just what you need to dry your dog quickly and efficiently, the micro-fiber material soaks up wet and mud from even the largest dog and cleans and dries your pet. Easily machine washable and long-lasting ( Do not use softener in the wash)
Buy 2 or 3 and always have one handy!

fields.name: Ergo Pin Brush
fields.description: The Ergo Pin Brush can be used for grooming any length of coat. Quickly de-tangles and removes dirt and loose soil in your pets hair, without pulling. Brush is easily cleaned and can be washed with soap and warm water. A great tool to keep handy

fields.name: Lickimat Buddy
fields.description: The Lickimat Buddy is the newest and most versatile of the Lickimat range.!   Recommended by animal behaviourists  and trainers to create interest and keep your pet from wolfing down their food. The Lickimat Buddy is strong and pliable -- is dishwasher safe and  durable. A quality item made to last.

fields.name: Cat Swipe Toy
fields.description: This Cat toy will give your pet hours of entertainment when you are not around. Prevent boredom and bad behaviours and stimulate your cat. Easy to put together and durable. No small parts and safety tested.

fields.name: Bowl and Fountain Combo
fields.description: Pet perfect!  Get this super cat fountain and bowl for all your cat's needs - comes with a washable rubber mat to keep splashes and crumbs off your floor. The fountain supplies running water that your pet will love! Easy to set up and safety tested
